order_number.orig_str: शासन निर्णय क्रमांकः स्थापना-२०२४/ प्र.क्र.२४१/ आरोग्य-४

para_trans: Fun five-pillar, Ta. Regarding sanction of new Primary Health Centre at Paranda, G. Dharashiv as a special case.
Government Decision No: Establishment-2024 / P.No.241 / Health-4

Read: - Letter No. of Joint Director, Health Services, (Pre-Centre / Sub-Centre / Dispensaries), Mumbai: Go to No. AASE / Room 7A / T-5 / Panchpipla / Pre-Centre / Approved / Dharashiv / 2742-44, dated 11.07.2024.
Introduction: - Mouje Paanchpipla, Ta. Health facilities to the residents of the locality at Paranda, Dist. Dharashiv
A new primary health centre needs to be sanctioned in line with the provision of primary health care at the site.
The issue of sanctioning a health centre was under the consideration of the government. The following decisions are being taken in this regard:
Government Decision: - Mouje Panchpipla, Ta. New Primary Health Centre at Paranda, Dist. Dharashiv as a "Special Case"
The Government decision is available on the Government of Maharashtra website www.maharashtra.gov.in.
